{"tid":2264084,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"44歲男無源頭染疫 為中聯辦宿舍住客 曾無戴罩行山","createTime":"2020-10-30T10:54:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T11:42:56.000Z","uid":239336,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"964066be7b06bd4a8149bad65a2fbabed391173d","tid":2264084,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T10:54:47.000Z","msg":"本港再現源頭不明個案。本港今日（30日）錄得7宗確診個案，唯一一宗本地個案屬源頭不明，是相隔4日再有源頭不明個案。其餘6宗為輸入個案。<br />\n<br />\n無源頭確診患者為44歲男子，居於北角清華街10-16號，為中聯辦員工宿舍地址，疑為中聯辦員工。患者於信德中心西座任文職工作，平日坐公司車上下班，公司有為員工安排定期病毒測試，曾在10月9日為員工安排測試，對上一次測試是在10月28日，40多位員工結果均呈陰性，只有今日確診男子呈陽性。衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君表示，患者在10月29日最後上班，當日得悉自己初步陽性，其後回想到早於27日有感覺疲倦，惟沒有上呼吸道病徵，當時未有特別留意，防護中心將當日定為個案患者開始發病日。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201030/I3JTV4QZ3FFQ5MYFKAUS5PM4WA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201030%2FI3JTV4QZ3FFQ5MYFKAUS5PM4WA%2F&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdtB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=31c1d4c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201030%2FI3JTV4QZ3FFQ5MYFKAUS5PM4WA%2F&h=41f368eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201030/I3JTV4QZ3FFQ5MYFKAUS5PM4WA/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa26c2b299b79d6241d98f01f9988128b6053c68","tid":2264084,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T10:56:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b31